assertions.notes:
Cannot fully test success payload without real Impartus credentials. Code inspection confirms the expected payload structure:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "status": "completed",
    "outputPaths": ["/path/to/video1.mp4", ...],
    "lectureCount": 5
  },
  "error": null,
  "meta": {"command": "download", "mode": "json"}
}
```
The payload provides terminal status ('completed'), all output file paths, and count for OpenClaw to act on.
